g-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Su_dung_dich_vu_doi_voi_Ads_Google_ban_se_nhan_duoc_loi_ich_sau\" title=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ads Google b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i \u00edch sau:\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ads Google b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i \u00edch sau:<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Nham_dung_doi_tuong_khach_hang_tiem_nang\" title=\"Nh\u1eafm \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng\">Nh\u1eafm \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Hieu_qua_cao_-_chi_phi_toi_uu\" title=\"Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao \u2013 chi ph\u00ed t\u1ed1i \u01b0u\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao \u2013 chi ph\u00ed t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Nhanh_chong_va_de_dang_quan_ly_dieu_khien\" title=\"Nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n\">Nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#He_thong_bao_cao_thong_ke_cap_nhat_chinh_xac\" title=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Quy_trinh_dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_cua_A_Chau_Media_duoc_thuc_hien_cu_the_nhu_sau\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:\">Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_tai_cac_tinh_mien_Trung_cua_Achaumedia_bao_gom\" title=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u1ee7a Achaumedia bao g\u1ed3m:\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u1ee7a Achaumedia bao g\u1ed3m:<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/#Chung_toi_cam_ket_voi_ban_khi_su_dung_dich_vu_chay_quang_cao_Ads_Google_cua_chung_toi\" title=\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Ads Google c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i:\u00a0\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Ads Google c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i:\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, PR, ch\u1ea1y ads gi\u00fap cho vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p tr\u1edf n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Trong c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi\u00a0<em><strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13152\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google-300x157.jpeg\" alt=\"d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y ads google\" width=\"850\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google-300x157.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google-768x402.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.jpeg 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i m\u00e0 Google cung c\u1ea5p cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 hay th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u,\u2026 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Google Adwords c\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c click v\u00e0o. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean trang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang web thu\u1ed9c m\u1ea1ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Google, th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1eeb kho\u00e1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Google Adwords n\u00f3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 website b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a Google m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n SEO t\u1eeb kho\u00e1. T\u1ee9c l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n cho Google \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd cho website b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a Google.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <em><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-affiliates-tai-hai-phong-xu-huong-kiem-tien-tai-nha.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Affiliates t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_dang_dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_co_the_ke_den_nhu\"><\/span><strong>C\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Google Ads hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 5 d\u1ea1ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ch\u00ednh:<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quang_cao_tim_kiem_Google_Search\"><\/span><strong>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm Google Search<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm =&gt; ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a tr\u00ean Google.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1eabu qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng khi h\u1ecd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 1 t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3\u00a0<em>(B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp)<\/em>.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Google_Display_Network_GDN\"><\/span><strong>Google Display Network (GDN)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>L\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o gi\u00fap t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u00f4i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c banner hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean c\u00e1c website n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Google.<\/p>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u1edf nh\u1eefng banner n\u00e0y s\u1ebd:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13158\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-display-network-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o google\" width=\"850\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-display-network-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-display-network.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f3 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh vi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Google c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i dung website m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111ang truy c\u1eadp.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng truy c\u1eadp, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd b\u00e1m \u0111u\u00f4i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Google Display Network c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t trong vi\u1ec7c g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u00e0 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd quan t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_Youtube_Ads\"><\/span><strong>Video Youtub<\/strong><strong>e Ads<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Youtube c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Google v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o, \u0111\u00e2y\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb video l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ecb so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13159\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/video-ytb-ads-300x158.png\" alt=\"video youtube ads\" width=\"850\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/video-ytb-ads-300x158.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/video-ytb-ads-768x404.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/video-ytb-ads.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf Google c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf qua vi\u1ec7c khai th\u00e1c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<p>GDN c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean Youtube, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n l\u00e0\u00a0<strong>Video Ads<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gmail_Ads\"><\/span><strong>Gmail Ads<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Gmail Ads l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1eeb Google,\u00a0\u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea7m trung &amp; \u0111\u1eaft ti\u1ec1n. V\u00ed d\u1ee5:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13160\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gmail-ads-300x124.jpg\" alt=\"gmails ads\" width=\"850\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gmail-ads-300x124.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/gmail-ads.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>B\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Xe c\u1ed9<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Trang s\u1ee9c<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Kh\u00f3a t\u1eadp gym<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>Kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/em><\/li>\n<li><em>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m s\u1ed1<\/em><\/li>\n<li>Du l\u1ecbch\/ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/li>\n<li><em>\u2026<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra Gmail Ads c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e1ch thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y ki\u1ec3m tra h\u1ed9p th\u01b0 Gmail th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Gmail Ads s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t mail g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c mail t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean kh\u00e1c, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong 2 tab\u00a0<strong>Social<\/strong>\u00a0&amp;\u00a0<strong>Promotions.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Google_Shopping_Ads\"><\/span><strong>Google Shopping Ads<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Google Shopping \u0111ang l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o cho nh\u1eefng doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 website tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn\u00a0<em>(online store)<\/em>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13163\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-shopping-ads-300x158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-shopping-ads-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-shopping-ads-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-shopping-ads-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/google-shopping-ads.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 Google x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng mua s\u1eafm tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm &amp; mua h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m c\u00e1c trang th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Amazon, Ebay\u2026<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_dung_dich_vu_doi_voi_Ads_Google_ban_se_nhan_duoc_loi_ich_sau\"><\/span><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Ads Google b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i \u00edch sau:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13156\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-300x174.png\" alt=\"ads\" width=\"850\" height=\"493\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-300x174.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads.png 730w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nham_dung_doi_tuong_khach_hang_tiem_nang\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eafm \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb ngay \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean trang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n cung c\u1ea5p, ho\u1eb7c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang m\u1ea1ng khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u01b0\u1edbt web m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau: khu v\u1ef1c, ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m,\u2026 m\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hieu_qua_cao_-_chi_phi_toi_uu\"><\/span><strong>Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao \u2013 chi ph\u00ed t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eafm m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Google Adwords gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n n\u00e2ng cao t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng, mang l\u1ea1i doanh thu cao v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1i \u0111a. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf, ch\u1ec9 khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng click v\u00e0o qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra. Google c\u00f2n cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch, gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n m\u1ee9c chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o theo ng\u00e0y, n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau h\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. V\u00ec v\u1eady, chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec3u qu\u1ea3 cao nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhanh_chong_va_de_dang_quan_ly_dieu_khien\"><\/span><span id=\"Nhanh_chong_va_de_dang_quan_ly,_dieu_khien\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch Google, qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n sau 5 ph\u00fat ngay khi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i dung qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, b\u1ed5 sung t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u00f3a ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch hay \u0111i\u1ec3u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n. Qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Google Adwords cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch theo b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef n\u00e0o, t\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"He_thong_bao_cao_thong_ke_cap_nhat_chinh_xac\"><\/span><span id=\"He_thong_bao_cao,_thong_ke_cap_nhat_chinh_xac\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00e1o c\u00e1o, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn gi\u1eefa qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Google v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c. Google cung c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean 50 lo\u1ea1i b\u00e1o c\u00e1o ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1eeb t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch, cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng nh\u00f3m qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a, khu v\u1ef1c, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m,\u2026 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng theo d\u00f5i s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_cua_A_Chau_Media_duoc_thuc_hien_cu_the_nhu_sau\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13153\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google-300x183.jpg\" alt=\"ch\u1ea1y ads google\" width=\"850\" height=\"517\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google-300x183.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google-1024x623.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google-768x467.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google-1536x935.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/ads-google.jpg 1775w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00ean Google. vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c nhu c\u1ea7u, c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau. L\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p tham gia Google Ads ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o. M\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1y Google ads c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, website, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Theo d\u00f5i xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/li>\n<li>L\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho website c\u00f4ng ty.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch khi tri\u1ec3n khai nh\u1eb1m mang v\u1ec1 doanh s\u1ed1 cao nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u website v\u1ec1 n\u1ed9i dung c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/li>\n<li>B\u00e1o c\u00e1o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch theo t\u1eebng th\u00e1ng, \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 doanh thu t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-affiliates-ha-noi.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Affiliates t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Google t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n Trung nh\u01b0: <\/strong><em>Thanh Ho\u00e1, Ngh\u1ec7 An, H\u00e0 T\u0129nh, Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh, Qu\u1ea3ng Tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 Th\u1eeba Thi\u00ean-Hu\u1ebf, \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, Qu\u1ea3ng Ng\u00e3i, B\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ecbnh, Ph\u00fa Y\u00ean, Kh\u00e1nh Ho\u00e0, Ninh Thu\u1eadn, B\u00ecnh Thu\u1eadn.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_chay_Ads_Google_tai_cac_tinh_mien_Trung_cua_Achaumedia_bao_gom\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u1ee7a Achaumedia bao g\u1ed3m:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 trong chi ti\u1ebft, v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng nh\u1ea5t<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng<\/li>\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u2013 H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng 24\/24h<\/li>\n<li>Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch nh\u01b0: s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3, li\u00ean k\u1ebft m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng trong qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chung_toi_cam_ket_voi_ban_khi_su_dung_dich_vu_chay_quang_cao_Ads_Google_cua_chung_toi\"><\/span><strong>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Ads Google c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i:\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13157\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-11-300x132.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-11-300x132.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/achaumedia-11.png 338w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u website<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u201cch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o\u201d, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft Digital Marketing t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, l\u1ea5y Google l\u00e0m trung t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>L\u00e0m s\u00e2u, chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a, gi\u00fap hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean t\u1eebng chi ph\u00ed b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf ra, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00e1c l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed, remarketing \u0111\u00fang h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh, gi\u00fap ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn l\u1ea1i 98% kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng t\u1eebng v\u00e0o website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mua h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ti\u00ean phong trong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb Google (AI, Machine Learning\u2026,) mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a\u2026 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy tr\u00ecnh h\u00f3a nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Chuy\u00ean gia<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>C\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111am m\u00ea v\u1edbi Google, t\u01b0 duy t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, 100% chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9\u00a0<em><strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google<\/strong><\/em> t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, PR, ch\u1ea1y ads gi\u00fap cho vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p tr\u1edf n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Trong c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi\u00a0d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google\u00a0c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e0&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13154,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[86,78],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Trong c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi\u00a0d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea1y Ads Google\u00a0c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chay-ads-google.html\/\" \/>\n<me